desc: UK based online children and babies concept store. Shop the worlds best sustainable brands from all over the world. Eco-friendly, ethical and premium products for children and parents. 10% off first order. Next day delivery available. Free delivery over £50.

layout.text: Dylan + Dora is the online home to a range of award-winning children's products which use natural, sustainable, and bio-degradable materials (#nonastychemicals) and brands that meet parents and their children at every stage!
